name: Bridge
details: Activate your core and posterior chain (a fancy term for the backside of your body) with a bridge. This is a great exercise to use as a warmup.

name: Chair squat
details: Squat to strengthen your legs and core, which will make everyday movements easier. Starting with a chair underneath you will help you master proper form.

name: Knee pushup
details: A beginner-style pushup, this move will help you build strength before attempting a standard pushup.

name: Stationary lunge
details: Hit your quads, hamstrings, and glutes with a stationary lunge.

name: Plank to Downward Dog
details: This move will test your upper body, especially your shoulders. Who says you need weights for a shoulder workout?

name: Bird Dog
details: A full-body move that requires balance and stability, the Bird Dog pose is easily scalable to your ability level. Start with this version if youâ€™re a beginner.
